\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ:<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/STR_Rail\" target=\"_blank\"> ꜱᴛʀ_ʀᴀɪʟ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"opC8HKcwLSAGD6w8enkKE.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2901,"messages":45113,"created_at":"2025-09-05T20:16:13.911925+00:00"}